These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, dog, pony, goat
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, purple, azure, aquamarine
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, old-henry, baccarat, blend
There 4 different types of food: cherry, pumpkin, garlic, papaya
 1. the old-henry-smoker is not to the right of the montecristo-smoker##8
 2. the person eating cherry is not to the left of the person eating cherry##8
 3. the person eating papaya is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the montecristo-smoker is not to the left of the blend-smoker##8
 5. the person eating cherry is not to the right of the person eating cherry##8
 6. the person who likes azure is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
 7. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 8. the person who likes aquamarine is between the person eating pumpkin and the old-henry-smoker##2
 9. the person eating papaya is the person who likes azure##1
10. the person eating papaya is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
11. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3
12. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5
13. the person who likes azure is not to the left of the person eating papaya##8
14. the owner of the dog is the person eating garlic##1
15. the owner of the dog is not the old-henry-smoker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Pet         | guinea-pig     | dog   | goat | pony |
| Color   | purple | aquamarine   | white   | azure  |
| Cigar         | old-henry  | baccarat  | blend  | montecristo |
| Food     | cherry    | garlic | pumpkin     | papaya    |

