.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, january, june, december
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, game, alhambra, pall-mall
4 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, whist, bridge
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, colombian, brazilian, argentine
 1. the person playing whist is between the egyptian and the person playing scrabble##2
 2. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the right of the colombian##8
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the montecristo-smoker##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the right of the argentine##8
 5. the egyptian is not to the left of the person playing scrabble##8
 6. the pall-mall-smoker is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##8
 7. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the argentine##5
 8. the brazilian is in an odd position##4
 9. the person playing snooker is the colombian##1
10. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
11. the egyptian is not to the left of the person playing whist##8
12. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
13. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the game-smoker##5
14. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
15. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left or far right##3
16. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
17. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the right of the person playing scrabble##8
18. the game-smoker is not to the right of the colombian##8
19. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Birthday      | october | june | december  | january  |
| Cigar          | pall-mall     | game | montecristo | alhambra  |
| Game   | scrabble    | whist  | bridge | snooker |
| Nationality           | brazilian | argentine | egyptian    | colombian  |

