 3. the fan of reggae is the owner of the goat##1
 4. the fan of pop is between the owner of the goldfish and the owner of the snake##2
 5. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
 6. the person traveling to london is not to the right of the fan of pop##8
 7. the chaman-smoker is in an odd position##4
 8. the davidoff-smoker is somewhere to the right of the aristoff-smoker##5
 9. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
10. the owner of the snake is the person traveling to london##1
11. the person traveling to paris is not to the right of the fan of classical##8
12. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
13. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
14. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
15. the aristoff-smoker is in an odd position##4

