The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, train, airplane, bike
 1. the dancer is not to the left of the person who likes coral##8
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who likes red##1
 3. the person driving the train is not the person who likes coral##6
 4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the lawyer##1
 5. the dancer is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##8
 6. the person driving the airplane is not to the right of the dancer##8
 7. the person driving the train is not to the left of the person who likes red##8
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is the project-manager##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the left of the person who likes black##8
10. the lawyer is not to the left of the dancer##8
11. the person driving the bike is between the person who likes black and the project-manager##2
12. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
13. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the right of the project-manager##8
14. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the project-manager##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
