 3. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##8
 4. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5
 5. the person who's hobby is chess is the person eating avocado##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the right of the person eating lime##8
 7. the owner of the hamster is not the person eating broccoli##6
 8. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere between the person who's hobby is chess and the owner of the hamster##7
 9. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the person who likes fuchsia##5
10. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who likes fuchsia##3
11. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
12. the person who likes fuchsia is not the person eating artichoke##6
13. the person eating lime is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
14. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
15. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the right of the person who likes fuchsia##8

.:: Answer ::.
